data.description: Uncover your ideal home in the heart of Lookingglass Heights! This spacious three-bedroom, two-bathroom split-entry gem is a must-see, conveniently close to Offutt AFB, shopping, and a lively park with a splash pad. With three living areas, a chic formal dining space, and a roomy back deck, entertaining is a breeze. Enjoy the bright and open flow of the main floor, complemented by vaulted ceilings and large windows. The lower level adds extra living space, a non-conforming bedroom, and a sizable storage area with potential for a lower-level bath. Abundant space and ready for a new owner - don't miss out!
